---
import MetaPage from "@/components/MetaPage.astro"
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro"
import { Image } from "astro:assets"
import profilePic from "@/assets/myprofilepic.jpg"
---

<Layout>
  <MetaPage slot="head" title="About" description="Who is 0xAkr4m? Red Teamer, AI Security Enthusiast, and a Vagabond of the digital age." />

  <prose-content>
    <h1 transition:name="about-title">About</h1>

    <about-hero>
      <Image
        src={profilePic}
        alt="0xAkr4m"
        width={200}
        height={200}
      />
    </about-hero>

    <h2>whoami</h2>
    <p>
      Yo. I'm <strong>0xAkr4m</strong>. I break things professionally as a Red Teamer and research AI security because the future needs stress-testing before it ships. 
    </p>

    <h2>what I do</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Red Teaming</strong> — Finding the holes in systems before the bad guys do.</li>
      <li><strong>AI Security</strong> — Prompt injection, bypasses, and making models behave unexpectedly.</li>
      <li><strong>CTFs</strong> — Continuously learning by solving labs.</li>
      <li><strong>Writing</strong> — Documenting the journey so others (and future me) can learn from the process.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>the vibe</h2>
    <p>
      This blog is heavily inspired by Miyamoto Musashi and the
      <em>Vagabond</em> manga by Takehiko Inoue. The philosophy is simple: master your craft, stay curious, and always keep learning.
    </p>

    <h2>connect</h2>
    <p>
      Want to collaborate or chat?
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/KaidAkram" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@KaidAkram</a></li>
      <li>Telegram: <a href="https://t.me/akramkd17" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@akramkd17</a></li>
      <li>LinkedIn: <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/akram-kaid/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Akram Kaid</a></li>
      <li>Discord: <a href="https://discordapp.com/users/akramkaid_27366" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@akramkaid_27366</a></li>
    </ul>

    <blockquote>
      <p>
        "There is nothing outside of yourself that can ever enable you to get
        better, stronger, richer, quicker, or smarter. Everything is within."
      </p>
      <p>— Miyamoto Musashi</p>
    </blockquote>
  </prose-content>
</Layout>

<style>
  about-hero {
    display: block;
    margin-block-end: var(--space-m);

    :global(img) {
      width: 140px;
      height: 140px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-full, 50%);
      border: 2px solid var(--border);
      object-fit: cover;
      filter: contrast(1.1) grayscale(10%);
    }
  }
</style>
